{"tid":1507510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［幫推］屋村噏耷冷門中學生有野同名校仔講","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:06.000Z","uid":187543,"like":457,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"76114d791130613a7fe796822a285c764d151eab","tid":1507510,"uid":187543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:16.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月，罷考上報得喇沙，東華三院聯合十幾間學校先有小小聲，皇仁仔一出po就個個打飛機，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有無諗過罷課要全港性先夠大聲吖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係話因為你地名校係協恩係拔萃定喇沙定華仁皇仁，所以就要話你地攞光環。<br />\n<br />\n而係國難當前，你地係名校當然本身有光環係度，可唔可以好好利用而唔係圍爐。根本今次罷課分開兩邊搞，一邊係某組織聯合港九名校一邊係大專聯合其他中學，冇人理嗰d紅底學校點反對學生搞罷課，咁樣分同買屎自己食有咩分別。可唔可以有自知自明，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好浪費自己光環淨係叫自己學校同學響應你地</span>，而係用你地聯合一齊既光環呼籲全港中學生，同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫東華三院保良局等等紅底學校既中學生</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係個個好似你哋咁，學校咁輕易應承俾你哋罷課。<br />\n利申:代友po"},{"pid":"c52c8871e7364c525b28eebfd654b01bdaf53117","tid":1507510,"uid":187543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"ded6230de15d3ad49e21cef7d2da6d8b43fd514d","tid":1507510,"uid":187543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:41.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"d594d345cb63e7cd90b42cf0379a1dba4c58dac0","tid":1507510,"uid":187543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"617dbe98056892643872cd3ed66135f0684aaeb6","tid":1507510,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=01e91b95\" data-au